<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm I. von Limburg-Broich</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe der Habe des Georg I. Tetzel, da ihn keine Schuld am Tod des Fuhrmanns trifft.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_339" id="168v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_339_r1l1">Dem Edeln vvolgeporen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l2"><expan>Junkh<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von <expan>Lẏmp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒum pruch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_339_r1l3">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gebeten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l4"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Jörgen Tecʒels <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers wegen ~ vvie vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l5">der fürbraht hab / daʒ Jm ewr Edel ſein hab vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l6">aufgehalten vnd genomen hab . darümb . daʒ der furman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l7">der Jm <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein habe gefüret 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd in ewr gepiete braht </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l9">hab / vnter dem 
<del rend="strikethrough">karren </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_line_1577278484333_1840">pferd </ab></add> tod funden ſey worden / daran doch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l10">der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . cʒemal kein ſchulde hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd Er habe auch </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein habe in ew <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> gepiete cʒu Geyen </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_line_1577278502222_1857">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒollet</expan> / </del> Vnd alſo maint der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> vnſer burger / ſölt Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l14">ſein hab 
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo verliſen darümb </del> von des 
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_line_1577278504267_1862"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> furmans wegen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_line_1577278506193_1867">
<del rend="strikethrough">darumb </del></ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ der </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l16">
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo abgangen iſt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_r1l15">als der </ab></add> von gotes gewalt / oder <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> eÿgen ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l18"><expan>vvarlaſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wegen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_r1l17"><expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt verlıſen </ab></add> daʒ Jm daran gar <expan>vngütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geſchehe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l19">Hyrümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr / dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger darynne ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l20">
<del rend="strikethrough"> gunſt vnd </del> gnade 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> beweiſen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wöllet </del> / vnd Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l22"> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein hab vnd kauffmanſchaft / 
<del rend="strikethrough">gnediklıch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_339_r1l21"><expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab></add> volgen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l23">laſſen vvöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> . Alſo . daʒ Er 
<del rend="strikethrough"> darynne </del> <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l24">vnſchulde 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan></del> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete darynne gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_339_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">wilicklıch </del> genẏſſe . das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_339" id="168v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln wolgeporen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                            <expan>junkh<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czum Pruch</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell
            vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gebeten
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Jörgen Teczels, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
            burgers wegen, wie uns der fürbraht hab, daz im ewr edel sein hab und
                <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> aufgehalten und genomen hab darümb, daz der
            furman, der im <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein habe gefüret hab, unter dem
              <add>pferd</add> tod funden sey worden, daran doch der
              <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> czemal kein schulde hab, und also maint der
                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> unser burger, sölt er sein hab von des
                  <add><expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> furmans wegen <add>als der</add> von
            gotes gewalt oder <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> eygen
              <expan>verwarlasu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<add><expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, verlisen</add>, daz im daran gar
                <expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geschehe. Hyrümb
            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger darynne ewr gnade beweisen und im
                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein hab und kauffmanschaft
                  <add><expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und</add> volgen lassen wöllet durch
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, also daz er <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> unschulde und
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> bete darynne gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel
            genysse. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
